{"id":314626,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-山东15名村民联名举报村主任贪污/","date":"2013-09-22T08:18:14Z","modified":"2013-09-22T08:18:14Z","title":"维权网 | 山东15名村民联名举报村主任贪污","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员一文报道）山东省威海荣成市滕家镇二章村村民，在今年一月份开始联名举报村主任肖振刚贪污一百多万元，至今无人过问。在多方投诉无果之下，特发表如下声明：我们所说的完完全全是事实、如有半点谎言、欺骗、捏造，我们</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>人愿负一切法律责任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>位村民的联系举报中写道：我们将山东省威海荣成市滕家镇二章村村委会主任肖振刚的贪污行为汇报给上级领导，他几年时间内在一个穷山沟子村收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>余万家产，请领导责成有关部门查证处理，我们提出以下事件请相关机构核实查办：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、肖振刚在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">04</span><span>年至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">05</span><span>年卖建筑用沙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>万多方、每方</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>元共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>万元、钱不知去向。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、肖振刚在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">04</span><span>年至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">05</span><span>年开具</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>万余元假柴油发票报销</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年一天的晚上肖振刚用赤山拉沙自卸车把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>吨铜管偷走、价值</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>万、（铜管数量有帐可查）。村委账面无款项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年肖振刚卖地挖沙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>余亩、钱不知去向、村委账面无款项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2021</span><span>年肖振刚私自卖老果园地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>多亩、村委账面无款项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、十台脱谷机、动力机、电机、废钢铁、油罐。大型拖拉机、连轨车各一台、三台联合收割机、电缆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span>米、卖的钱不知去向、村委账面无款项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>、挖沙毁掉树木</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span>余棵、树木钱数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多万元、卖的钱不知去向、村委账面无款项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、叫标地款、卖山岗共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>万元不知去向、村委账面无款项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>以上是村民反映的一部分肖振刚贪污行为，村民提供相关线索、有事实证据、可到现场指证。村民实名举报签名：肖文斋、肖辉晓、肖模考、肖国林、肖占、肖模紧、肖辉永、肖群英、肖国进、肖新东、肖国仁、肖建强、肖建忠、肖国新、肖国福。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}